{"tid":2227870,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文匯報：護旗手劏房戶賣樓捐獻近百萬元抗疫　出錢撐警拆連儂牆","createTime":"2020-10-03T06:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T17:09:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7771dbb57332426d23f2d61ddd783a4209102575","tid":2227870,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"《文匯報》的報道指，徐天民一家三口以 4500 元租住深水埗 70 呎唐四樓劏房，本來曾打算「搬大啲」，但因「睇唔過眼」有人破壞和燒國旗等，「自發」舉五星旗上街，又「組織愛國力量」，出錢舉辦撐警、護旗、清連儂牆等活動，用了超過 10 萬積蓄，到今年初疫情爆發，徐天民積蓄已快用完，但他賣掉內地的房子，用了幾十萬元買防疫物資捐給家鄉，「我喝家鄉水，吃家鄉米長大，自然要回報家鄉！」<br />\n<br />\n徐天民又聲稱自己多次上街後被「黑暴」點相，和家人都被起底，經常收到威脅電話，甚至稱有「黑暴」上門踢門，到去年 10 月他任職的酒樓擔心被連累要求他離職，他其後一直找不到飲食業工作，改到地盤做散工，「好多餐廳都怕被（黑暴）『裝修』（破壞），邊有人敢請我？」但《文匯》引述他表示「無悔為正義力量發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》形容徐天民「對報效祖國從不吝嗇」，用畢生近百萬積蓄助內地抗疫，體現了駱惠寧所指「愛國不是一種選擇，而是一種義務」，又引述徐天民指，獲駱惠寧家訪心情激動，「證明我哋平時愛國愛港，做有益社會嘅事，係好有意義，有可能受到中聯辦關注。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A0%B1%E6%95%88%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1-%E8%AD%B7%E6%97%97%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E6%8D%90%E7%8D%BB%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E5%87%BA%E9%8C%A2%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%86%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%258D%2590%25E7%258D%25BB%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=8202249e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%258D%2590%25E7%258D%25BB%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586%2F&h=62476000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A0%B1%E6%95%88%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1-%E8%AD%B7%E6%97%97%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E6%8D%90%E7%8D%BB%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E5%87%BA%E9%8C%A2%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%86%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86/</a>"},{"pid":"90af7c27418167e04dfc29f4c636c3b3bac7e357","tid":2227870,"uid":53687,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"係時候鬥藍，唔肯捐錢畀祖國都係偽藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17747916860798f26f8a3a0bc708834d7c1d0dc1","tid":2227870,"uid":215611,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"有一百萬唔洗住劏房啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ded21b5fedf3a18da0b7e7bfb572479e82ae972","tid":2227870,"uid":91721,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"90af7c27418167e04dfc29f4c636c3b3bac7e357","tid":2227870,"uid":53687,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"係時候鬥藍，唔肯捐錢畀祖國都係偽藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"住劏房都捐到一百萬<br />\n<br />\n你哋住公屋私屋唔係唔捐下話"},{"pid":"9da6e72048dca552b9b4c8a24265c5641e670a66","tid":2227870,"uid":42687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"做得好！抵讚！所有愛祖國既兒女都應該盡獻身家救國！<br />\n呢啲真係榜樣， 煲大佢，send去咩savehk叫佢哋跟機啦！"},{"pid":"084661f29f3c043e3f7e229b9